# Cursor rules (this repository)

Read **AGENTS.md** at the repository root. Treat **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** as binding (respect `alwaysApply: true` and **globs**).

After **`git push`**, monitor GitHub Actions for that commit before treating the task as finished.

If you make functional UI changes, always test them using the dev panel at **http://panel.dev.kaiad.dev**.

Do not skip verification, CI monitoring, or project rules because the task looks small.
